results of a FlyMine query.	Working with lists:\
\
{\listtext	\'95	}Upload a mixed list of identifiers and convert it to a list of gene symbols.\
{\listtext	\'95	}For any list of genome annotation features export their sequences or locations\
{\listtext	\'95	}Find out which genes are unique between different lists\
{\listtext	\'95	}Find all genes that particular species have in common\
{\listtext	\'95	}Export a list of gene identifiers to FlyBase\
{\listtext	\'95	}Convert a list to a different type, for example genes to mRNAs, exons or proteins}

